    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246790/extras/1f3c7d39905784033d7258cd5543cedb.poster.avif?t=1734609480\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246790/extras/1f3c7d39905784033d7258cd5543cedb.webm?t=1734609480\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246790/extras/1f3c7d39905784033d7258cd5543cedb.mp4?t=1734609480\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Great Alps</strong> is an expansion to<strong> Peaks of Yore.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Enter the Alpine Mountaineering Scene</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take the Alpine Express and travel to the picturesque Einvald Valley to conquer the Great Alps' challenging collection of crags, boulders, mountains, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>A member of the <strong>Alpine Climbing Association</strong> will be tracking your progress, and provide you with ample challenge as you progress.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246790/extras/1fc150c4bd6c5c096ab2266f6f77a07b.poster.avif?t=1734609480\" width=598 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246790/extras/1fc150c4bd6c5c096ab2266f6f77a07b.webm?t=1734609480\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246790/extras/1fc150c4bd6c5c096ab2266f6f77a07b.mp4?t=1734609480\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A Mountaineer Turned Alpinist</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bring along your acquired climbing gear from the <strong>Great Gales</strong> as you venture onto the great Alpine peaks. New locations will test your knowledge in all forms of climbing. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246790/extras/145ffff9e60ac523cb52662f1d28fc18.poster.avif?t=1734609480\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246790/extras/145ffff9e60ac523cb52662f1d28fc18.webm?t=1734609480\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246790/extras/145ffff9e60ac523cb52662f1d28fc18.mp4?t=1734609480\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Perfect Your Grasp on New Rock Holds</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Memorize your approach on Volumes, train your balancing skills on both Finger and Palm Cracks, and finesse your precision on Pinches. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your patience and skills will be put to the test as you explore many new holds alongside those familiar to you from the Great Gales.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246790/extras/a85d941ba7e48a83dfa83ebe7e2bb76e.poster.avif?t=1734609480\" width=600 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246790/extras/a85d941ba7e48a83dfa83ebe7e2bb76e.webm?t=1734609480\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246790/extras/a85d941ba7e48a83dfa83ebe7e2bb76e.mp4?t=1734609480\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Climb <strong>23 scenic new challenging locations</strong>, accessible from the quaint cabin provided to you by the <strong>Alpine Climbing Association</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master a slew of <strong>new hold types</strong>. Test your balance on <strong>cracks</strong>, and strengthen your precision on <strong>pinches</strong> and <strong>volumes</strong>. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect summit <strong>stamps </strong>from each peak, and find <strong>elusive creatures and flowers</strong> native to the Great Alps.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Conquer special challenges to collect <strong>12 unique ornate sleeve pins</strong> to adorn your tweeds.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover a plethora of new discoverable collectibles that <strong>alter the gameplay</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set new summit and time records, and earn well-deserved rewards.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy the serene and picturesque quietudes of the Great Alps.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246790/extras/748e2e30f2ce05a31a5ff2b48650331f.avif?t=1734609480\" width=600 height=254 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>*The Great Alps requires the base game product Peaks of Yore.</i></p>",
